Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.11,0:00:12.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}合宿之後一周
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.20,0:00:18.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}正是暑假 發生了件不得了的事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.09,0:01:57.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這裡就是猿島家麼
