Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.80,0:02:01.72,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(579,628)}{\fad(300,300)}第 7 話  『只要不是天婦羅就好！』
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.02,0:00:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.26,0:02:01.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 雖然和學生會的人來過好幾次
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.80,0:02:03.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是一次都沒有見過
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.72,0:02:04.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.89,0:02:07.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她是個連我們也感覺非常棘手的家裡蹲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.23,0:02:09.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}家裡蹲？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.27,0:02:13.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}恐怕是和魔女的能力有關
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.03,0:02:17.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小田切她們好像已經收集猿島的情報了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.36,0:02:18.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}豈不是已經被搶先了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.86,0:02:19.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要怎麼辦的 宮村
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.03,0:02:21.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嘛 冷靜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.78,0:02:22.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有招兒了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.66,0:02:26.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}強行突破
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.75,0:02:27.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}冷靜 山田
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.08,0:02:28.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Hi guys
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.37,0:02:30.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.08,0:02:32.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}猿島？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.96,0:02:33.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是這個人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.34,0:02:35.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這人哪裡像家裡蹲啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.38,0:02:40.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對了 有件事想請你們幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.97,0:02:47.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}話說 為什麼我們要來重新佈置房間
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.43,0:02:48.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這也是沒辦法的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.35,0:02:52.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}順利的話 說不定能問出猿島的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.23,0:02:54.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那你也來搬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.27,0:02:56.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}知道了 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.57,0:02:59.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哦 這可是個好東西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.86,0:03:02.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這面積真是美好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.28,0:03:03.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你TM快去幹活
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.12,0:03:07.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 猿島 都弄完了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.04,0:03:09.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼你在睡覺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.46,0:03:10.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.67,0:03:13.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}站住 山田
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.83,0:03:16.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你看看 你看看 這傢伙哪裡像是個家裡蹲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.63,0:03:19.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哪像個因為啥煩惱而成為魔女的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.05,0:03:21.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}雖然不知道是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.13,0:03:24.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但怎麼想現在都是絕好的機會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.01,0:03:25.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}機會？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.60,0:03:27.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你快去親她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.52,0:03:29.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那樣有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.39,0:03:32.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你也幹不少活了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.10,0:03:35.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}倒不如就親一下 即使這樣她還欠你的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.11,0:03:38.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是這樣麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.32,0:03:38.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}必須的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.82,0:03:41.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣的話 就沒有辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.24,0:03:47.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可別怪我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.45,0:03:48.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}救我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.12,0:03:53.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}救我 山田
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.29,0:03:58.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}宮村 你能先回去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.05,0:03:59.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.59,0:04:01.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.30,0:04:05.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}剛剛把你當力工使喚 抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.76,0:04:08.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒事 你剛剛說的救我 是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.72,0:04:10.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}其實我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.93,0:04:12.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}知道什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.52,0:04:15.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我早就知道你會來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.36,0:04:17.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是聽誰說的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.07,0:04:22.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是的 我能看見未來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.70,0:04:26.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}能看見…未來？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.95,0:04:27.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.37,0:04:30.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你腦子沒什麼問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.87,0:04:33.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你不相信也可以理解
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.54,0:04:36.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不過事實如此 你也不能不信
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.75,0:04:39.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不 應該說你只能相信了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.67,0:04:42.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.92,0:04:46.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}最開始的時候只能預見短暫的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.93,0:04:48.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}比如 下節課是自習
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.51,0:04:50.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}會有突擊考試什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.43,0:04:56.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}突然有一天 我看見到了可怕的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.19,0:05:00.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}舊校舍發生火災的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.53,0:05:06.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}然後我竟然成了縱火犯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.16,0:05:09.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}相信我 不是我做的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.12,0:05:14.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以我就決定不去學校了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.29,0:05:18.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為這話對誰說都不會相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.75,0:05:20.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以就變成了家裡蹲？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.13,0:05:22.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是啊 猿島
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.67,0:05:26.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼你會說我只能相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.68,0:05:34.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為你也在火災現場
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.68,0:05:39.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你和我都被當成了犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.86,0:05:41.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啥 為啥會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.69,0:05:43.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}討厭 我也想知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.57,0:05:46.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}話雖如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.82,0:05:48.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不過這樣我就明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.37,0:05:55.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不去學校 也是為了不和你產生交集
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.50,0:05:59.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}像這樣和預見的未來一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.71,0:06:01.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我和你相遇了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.75,0:06:04.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這個時候 我是該道歉麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.42,0:06:09.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不用 該道歉的應該是我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.34,0:06:14.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}說不定這樣和你相遇 未來就會有所改變
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.93,0:06:18.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是未來不是這麼容易就能改變的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.60,0:06:20.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我說 猿島
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.90,0:06:22.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}和我接個吻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.86,0:06:27.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就因為把你捲進來 所以要我用身體來償還麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.61,0:06:28.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我沒說要到那個地步啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.20,0:06:30.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這麼做是另有深意的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.74,0:06:34.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}總之 要找的真正的犯人 只能用這個方法了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.12,0:06:34.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.50,0:06:39.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是山田的話 沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.33,0:06:41.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.33,0:06:44.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我最後的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.80,0:06:55.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒必要把舌頭伸進來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.56,0:06:57.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.56,0:06:59.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}無禮的傢伙 好好聽人說話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.73,0:07:05.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也就是說 猿島瑪利亞毫無疑問就是魔女了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.86,0:07:09.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}果然你們也無法掩飾驚訝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.36,0:07:14.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}其實關於她的能力 我已經大概清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.12,0:07:18.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不過我沒有告訴你們的義務
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.87,0:07:23.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只要我出手 這種事情就是輕鬆加愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.63,0:07:31.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.85,0:07:36.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼只打我？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.68,0:07:39.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哦 好厲害啊 山田
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.89,0:07:42.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你說會被小田切打 原來說的是這件事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.15,0:07:45.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}預知未來的能力真的是好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.90,0:07:46.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.40,0:07:50.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣就明確了猿島是能預知未來的魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.03,0:07:53.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}接下來就是正題了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.45,0:07:56.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大家先看一下這個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.95,0:08:00.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這就是爆炸啊 山田畫匠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.33,0:08:03.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你該不會真的預見到了這個畫面了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.12,0:08:06.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼可能 我看到的更加真實啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.54,0:08:09.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我是說舊校舍會發生火災
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.09,0:08:12.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我和猿島被當成犯人這件事才是重點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.55,0:08:15.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那的確是件大事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.84,0:08:16.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.68,0:08:18.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}既然已經預見到了未來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.51,0:08:20.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不快點找出真凶就糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.06,0:08:21.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}山田同學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.35,0:08:25.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}剛才你和宮村接吻時看到的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.15,0:08:27.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}能再告訴我一次嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.07,0:08:30.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}白石和伊藤俯視著我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.53,0:08:33.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我的臉上清楚的印著掌印
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.03,0:08:36.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣啊 也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.99,0:08:39.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}山田你能看見自己的樣子對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.04,0:08:41.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啊 那幅畫也是那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.41,0:08:44.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這個果然是山田
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.54,0:08:45.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你們把它當成是誰了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.33,0:08:48.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}然後當時宮村也在場嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.38,0:08:53.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這麼一說 宮村確實不在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.26,0:08:55.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}果然是這個樣子的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.84,0:08:59.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}和宮村接吻後預見的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.56,0:09:01.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看不到宮村
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.93,0:09:03.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這是代表什麼意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.06,0:09:05.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也許就是以宮村的視角看到的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.27,0:09:06.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}視角？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.02,0:09:07.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.23,0:09:12.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是說 接吻之後能以對方的視角預見到自己的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.45,0:09:15.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.82,0:09:17.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你那個表情絕對是沒有聽明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.16,0:09:19.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}再好好看一遍這幅畫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.37,0:09:23.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在裡面能看到山田和猿島 也就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.62,0:09:24.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.62,0:09:27.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 山田 你要去哪裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.46,0:09:30.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}火災現場還有另一個人？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.25,0:09:32.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.84,0:09:35.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}接過吻的物件中 你有沒有頭緒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.88,0:09:37.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有是有…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.72,0:09:40.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是有點不太好開口
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.43,0:09:44.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是我的男性朋友們…來著的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.73,0:09:45.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}男性朋友…們？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.39,0:09:47.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是 相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.44,0:09:49.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}並不是戀愛關係
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.35,0:09:52.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}同是歸國子女 碰巧關係比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.15,0:09:54.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為…為什麼和我解釋這麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.53,0:09:57.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}告訴我那傢伙的名字和住址
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.03,0:10:02.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好 但是 他該不會就是縱火犯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.04,0:10:04.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這個我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.16,0:10:07.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是 和火災有關係是肯定的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.46,0:10:09.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也…是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.58,0:10:11.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我去找他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.71,0:10:14.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你一步也不要離開家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.38,0:10:16.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.67,0:10:17.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是山田你要小心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.13,0:10:21.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是 因為山田和他見面了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.76,0:10:23.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}未來成了現實該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.31,0:10:29.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}椿劍太郎嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.65,0:10:34.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}厲害 這都做得到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.40,0:10:36.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你們可別小看真正的不良啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.99,0:10:38.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不良也無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.24,0:10:41.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在遊戲裡追求第一就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.12,0:10:42.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.74,0:10:45.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是的 可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.33,0:10:46.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.41,0:10:48.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 你是D班的椿劍太郎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.21,0:10:50.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}又輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.75,0:10:51.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}下場定輸贏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.04,0:10:52.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 你聽見沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.96,0:10:54.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}吵死了 別礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.13,0:10:57.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}別人說話你給我認真聽 椿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.17,0:11:00.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼了 你這混蛋 不是b班的山田嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.26,0:11:02.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}找我什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.89,0:11:04.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以說有事要問你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.68,0:11:08.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也有事要問你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.52,0:11:13.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你喜歡上白石了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.36,0:11:15.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不是歸國子女嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.73,0:11:17.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以經常被別人捧著
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.94,0:11:21.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}白石她對我不限一顧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.02,0:00:01.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}【這裡是OP~MS】
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.11,0:11:24.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這實在太新鮮了 讓我很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.62,0:11:27.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在那之後 我就喜歡上白石了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.41,0:11:30.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你真是個奇怪的傢伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.71,0:11:33.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以 我要向白石告白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.04,0:11:34.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.04,0:11:37.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明天 在學校的中庭拜託幫我把白石叫出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.55,0:11:40.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等…明天什麼的 也太突然了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.18,0:11:43.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這傢伙是認真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.05,0:11:47.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}雖然說實話我並不覺得白石會同意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.47,0:11:49.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.56,0:11:50.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啊 真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.31,0:11:53.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好人啊 山田
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.73,0:11:57.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是 這傢伙真的會在舊校舍放火嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.48,0:12:01.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我就對這樣的山田 透露下我的拿手絕活
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.11,0:12:06.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這個 在失落或者想要打起精神的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.24,0:12:07.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我是一定會做的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.75,0:12:10.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.37,0:12:14.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這裡不是學校的舊校舍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.04,0:12:16.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}火災發生的現場啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.30,0:12:19.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.22,0:12:24.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}烹飪…教室
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.56,0:12:37.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不管怎麼想 就是這貨沒跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.52,0:12:41.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}做好了 友情的見證
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.49,0:12:45.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是這傢伙引發的火災吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.07,0:12:47.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}誒 不吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.25,0:12:53.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}火災是今天？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.41,0:12:54.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.37,0:12:56.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你要來學校？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.54,0:13:01.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是啊 老師說明天務必到校
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.21,0:13:05.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}山田君 猿島同學 還有椿同學
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.76,0:13:08.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這三人今天最終還是在學校聚齊了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.93,0:13:11.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不管怎麼說都要阻止椿做天婦羅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.81,0:13:15.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}話說回來 失落的時候 吃天婦羅來打起精神是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.98,0:13:16.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是 山田
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.44,0:13:19.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}想想昨天小田切給你的那巴掌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.65,0:13:22.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你明明事先都知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.53,0:13:24.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼沒有辦法去改變
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.65,0:13:28.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你看到的未來 真的能被改變嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.04,0:13:33.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這…這樣只能去放手一搏了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.75,0:13:36.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你打算怎麼做 山田
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.34,0:13:41.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這不是山田嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.50,0:13:43.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}到底是怎麼一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.80,0:13:46.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}時間都到了白石還沒來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.84,0:13:48.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.14,0:13:49.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.68,0:13:53.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我連白都沒告就被甩了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.56,0:13:54.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是那個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.85,0:13:56.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.18,0:13:58.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼你會代替白石同學過來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.98,0:13:59.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}冷靜一下 椿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.90,0:14:02.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你仔細聽好我將要說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.61,0:14:07.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}和我 接吻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.53,0:14:12.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.08,0:14:15.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}果然我還是被甩了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.70,0:14:18.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你想要用玩笑來安慰我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.54,0:14:19.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}才不是玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.79,0:14:21.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我是認真的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.50,0:14:25.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我希望你能回應山田的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.71,0:14:27.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你這麼說更容易弄混了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.30,0:14:30.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是嗎 沒想到會是山田
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.30,0:14:32.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}隨你怎麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.10,0:14:35.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}和這傢伙交換 然後不去接近舊校舍的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.02,0:14:37.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}火災應該就不會發生了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.73,0:14:39.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}抱歉 我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.90,0:14:42.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我只對白石有感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.32,0:14:43.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.19,0:14:44.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}別介意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.78,0:14:46.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要說的好像我被甩了一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.86,0:14:48.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是的 這樣一來只能硬來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.49,0:14:50.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}上吧 宮村
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.45,0:14:50.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.24,0:14:53.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}趁現在 山田
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.41,0:14:56.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}抱歉 椿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.70,0:14:58.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這裡面有很深奧的緣由
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.58,0:15:03.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這傢伙挺強的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.01,0:15:09.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}做得到的話就來試試吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.84,0:15:11.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.01,0:15:13.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真快呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.64,0:15:15.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒想到椿那傢伙竟然這麼強
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.60,0:15:17.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}果然不行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.10,0:15:19.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}果然是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.14,0:15:22.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我就知道你們兩個會一身狼狽的回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.86,0:15:25.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我和伊藤同學接吻了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.73,0:15:26.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}猿…猿島？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.36,0:15:29.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小麗全部都告訴我了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.32,0:15:31.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}以前的事和魔女的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.57,0:15:35.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我還以為山田是自己一個人在努力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.95,0:15:37.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不…那個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.08,0:15:40.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}竟然還有這麼好的同伴 為什麼不告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.71,0:15:43.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你果然是樂天派啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.75,0:15:46.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是要怎麼辦才好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.71,0:15:48.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你沒能和椿交換吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.26,0:15:49.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.55,0:15:51.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣一來…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.43,0:15:55.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}白…白石 只能讓你接受他的告白了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.02,0:16:01.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不 我有更好的辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.52,0:16:03.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.02,0:16:05.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}椿君 等很久了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.98,0:16:07.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}白…白石同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.73,0:16:08.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不 完全沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.07,0:16:10.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也是剛到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.57,0:16:11.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.90,0:16:13.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我聽山田同學說了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.91,0:16:15.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你有話要對我說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.78,0:16:17.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.91,0:16:19.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}白石同學 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.20,0:16:22.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}從很久以前就對白石同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.16,0:16:23.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.83,0:16:27.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在那之前能聽一下我的願望嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.13,0:16:28.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.55,0:16:32.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我希望你現在能跟我一起去買東西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.13,0:16:35.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小雅的影像中出現了時鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.55,0:16:38.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這就是火災發生的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.97,0:16:40.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也就是說 在時間到來之前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.89,0:16:42.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}山田把椿帶出去就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.31,0:16:45.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}椿 怎…怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.02,0:16:47.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可以
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.36,0:16:49.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.44,0:16:51.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那麼趕快出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.19,0:16:54.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣應該就能改變未來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.12,0:17:00.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣就不能好好聊天了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.41,0:17:02.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.87,0:17:06.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好 就算是椿 在這種地方也不可能告白的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.21,0:17:11.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}能行 只要再在這裡逛一個小時…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.80,0:17:12.80,phone,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,320)\frz2.122}{\alpha&H04&}猿島瑪利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.80,0:17:12.80,phone,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,320)\frz2.122}{\blur11}猿島瑪利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.13,0:17:15.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是的 又有電話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.59,0:17:16.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.43,0:17:18.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}別說改變未來了 情況更加惡化了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.30,0:17:18.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.43,0:17:22.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}本來在活動室的小雅來到了火災現場
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.73,0:17:25.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你到底在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.27,0:17:28.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}抱歉 我等下再打給你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.36,0:17:30.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.19,0:17:31.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}事情我已經聽說了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.32,0:17:34.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 宮村 現在該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.86,0:17:35.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.70,0:17:39.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}起碼知道了 未來確實在改變
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.20,0:17:43.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可能是你們的身體互換改變了未來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.87,0:17:45.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.08,0:17:48.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}到這地步了沒辦法 用最後那招吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.54,0:17:52.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}既然不得不回應告白 索性就讓他延期吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.38,0:17:55.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.38,0:17:59.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對不起 剛剛開始一直電話不停
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.68,0:18:00.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有點急事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.97,0:18:03.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是我還什麼都沒說…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.10,0:18:07.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明天 再說吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.77,0:18:09.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}拜託 要答應啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.52,0:18:13.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}太好了 明天也能見到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.03,0:18:15.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好 沒有情緒低落
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.32,0:18:19.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 那我先趕時間
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.36,0:18:20.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等等 白石同學
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.50,0:18:27.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼樣 宮村
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.16,0:18:30.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你是白癡嗎 趕快離開那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.30,0:18:38.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼回事 這個浪漫氣氛爆棚的地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.63,0:18:40.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}白石同學
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.47,0:18:43.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等不到明天了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.81,0:18:47.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.98,0:18:51.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼 怎麼會變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.61,0:18:54.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.20,0:19:00.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}請和我交往吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.12,0:19:04.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}該怎麼回應…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.66,0:19:07.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣的話…對不起了白石…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.87,0:19:10.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.37,0:19:11.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可以等一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.63,0:19:14.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 白…不山田…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.46,0:19:18.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你為什麼會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.69,0:19:31.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.94,0:19:37.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們兩個 就是這種關係
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.53,0:19:44.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等等 椿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.28,0:19:47.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}白石你這傢伙 想做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.99,0:19:49.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只有這個辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.54,0:19:51.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}搞不懂你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.75,0:19:52.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}山田你去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.46,0:19:54.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還用說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.63,0:19:55.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}和他交換身體
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.34,0:20:02.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好了 快開門椿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.38,0:20:04.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}閉嘴山田 我再不相信任何人了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.35,0:20:08.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}先是被誘惑我的白石甩了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.10,0:20:10.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}又被身為好朋友的你背叛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.06,0:20:12.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都說了那是有原因的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.98,0:20:13.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.56,0:20:16.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}居然鎖上了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.23,0:20:19.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}拜託了 只有天婦羅千萬不要碰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.48,0:20:22.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}山田君 快離開這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.40,0:20:23.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}白石
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.20,0:20:27.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}白石同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.71,0:20:43.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}已經過了火災的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.26,0:20:46.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}成 成功了我們…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.97,0:20:50.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們 拯救了大家的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.35,0:20:53.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.49,0:21:05.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我和山田交換身體 原來是因為魔女的力量嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.78,0:21:07.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.03,0:21:08.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.53,0:21:12.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那讓我也加入超研部吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.41,0:21:14.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼要這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.96,0:21:17.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}經過這次我也對魔女的力量感興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.92,0:21:19.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是為了泡小麗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.63,0:21:22.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎 怎麼會 才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.80,0:21:25.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而且 絕對不允許你在這裡炸天婦羅
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.13,0:21:27.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an8\fs30}不是說了我是因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.30,0:21:28.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}山田
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.09,0:21:29.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an8\fs30}說不定就是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.26,0:21:30.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an8\fs30}怎麼能這麼霸道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.68,0:21:30.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}出來一下可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.22,0:21:34.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Thank you 山田
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.98,0:21:39.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不 不用在意 我也不想成為犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.48,0:21:41.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還害羞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.77,0:21:43.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是 有件事我比較在意
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.94,0:21:44.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.03,0:21:48.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}白石那傢伙 為什麼要這麼突然交換回來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.87,0:21:50.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你沒聽她說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.33,0:21:56.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我可做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.79,0:22:01.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}知道未來是那樣 還能義無反顧的交換
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.55,0:22:07.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是嗎 猿島同學告訴你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.47,0:22:08.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.84,0:22:12.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}白石她 不希望你成為犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.64,0:22:15.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.73,0:22:26.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒什麼 都過去了…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.49,0:22:28.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你以為我會這樣說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.37,0:22:31.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}別再做這種蠢事了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.55,0:22:50.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.10,0:22:56.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼這麼高興
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.60,0:23:00.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是領教到你的纏人了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.60,0:23:02.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an8\fs30}疼…疼…疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.85,0:23:04.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也是超研部的成員了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.57,0:23:06.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哎呀 大家都在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.44,0:23:11.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好消息 我終於知道猿島瑪利亞的能力了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.28,0:23:15.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}已經驚訝地說不出話了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.04,0:23:16.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}想知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.20,0:23:19.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}究竟說不說呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.21,0:23:28.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.17,0:23:30.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以說 為什麼只打我一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.39,0:23:34.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}早
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.47,0:23:37.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}第二學期開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.06,0:23:39.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}馬上就是文化祭了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.60,0:23:42.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}文化祭啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.77,0:23:48.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那…要玩點什麼呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.20,0:25:24.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我說 椿 我好想吃天福羅哦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.50,0:25:27.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不對 是天婦羅 天 婦 羅
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.13,0:25:28.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}請給我 天福羅
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.79,0:25:29.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.00,0:25:32.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}下集 山田君與七個魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.63,0:25:33.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}雖然很煩人
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.84,0:25:35.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是你的天福羅煩人
